{"tid":657884,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[搵旅伴]六月中至底10-14日伊朗遊","createTime":"2018-05-08T13:04:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-03T12:03:52.000Z","uid":128081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"223efaec0953d3c066380d158af3b7ec53a7dde3","tid":657884,"uid":128081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T13:04:55.000Z","msg":"小弟6月中尾想伊朗行下，即使冇旅伴都會自己去，當然有人一齊去可以多個照應，所以開post想睇下有冇巴絲有興趣一齊去<br />\n<br />\n有幾點：<br />\n1. 行程可以詳細傾，可以我安排，又可以你話事，唔啱講到啱，互相尊重<br />\n2. 盡量唔會豪華遊<br />\n3. 日子未完全定好，六月中前後一兩星期都可，但連機程應起碼10日，自己預時間<br />\n4. 有食煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，癮唔大，唔會影響到旅伴，想我果2星期唔食都可，出聲就ok<br />\n5. 唔想太多人，最後出發希望係1-4個<br />\n<br />\nSorry廢話好似講得有啲多，如果有興趣就留言或留TG<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37ab0157d174b9e78cfdb499c0b3390f09dba69e","tid":657884,"uid":156843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T13:10:17.000Z","msg":"巴打今年齋戒月16／開始，如果食煙要留意下"},{"pid":"a14e8a0f63edae1633cf73b10c1202c5f5d5b5b5","tid":657884,"uid":156843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37ab0157d174b9e78cfdb499c0b3390f09dba69e","tid":657884,"uid":156843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T13:10:17.000Z","msg":"巴打今年齋戒月16／開始，如果食煙要留意下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T13:10:33.000Z","msg":"16／5"},{"pid":"ef364171975c134704b1b55f4d14f66b4ed4c2b9","tid":657884,"uid":128081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37ab0157d174b9e78cfdb499c0b3390f09dba69e","tid":657884,"uid":156843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T13:10:17.000Z","msg":"巴打今年齋戒月16／開始，如果食煙要留意下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T15:22:55.000Z","msg":"唔該曬ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0e9883b303da6427331530dfcf464552a594f53","tid":657884,"uid":47470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T15:51:29.000Z","msg":"巴打定左？ 9-11月得唔得"},{"pid":"988498159c13ee3